Key Match Events: The match between USA and Ireland was called off due to wet outfield and rain in Florida, resulting in a shared point for both teams.
Post-Match Reflections: Babar Azam's Pakistan were knocked out of the tournament well before their final group game against Ireland on Sunday.
Miscellaneous Highlights: USA and Ireland shared a point each, with co-hosts USA qualifying for the Super Eight stage with five points after four games.
Others: Pakistan join New Zealand on the way out of the tournament, and USA's qualification to the Super Eight stage carries huge significance, ensuring their participation in the next T20 World Cup in 2026.
